subject: Hockey, Ice
lead_paragraph: Jason Strudwick scored on a two-on-one break 1 minute 40 seconds into overtime for the Rangers, who rallied from two goals down to beat the host Pittsburgh Penguins, 4-3, for their fifth straight victory.
